Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:18.29,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:21.74,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:25.15,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:28.50,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:38.62,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:42.21,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:45.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:52.21,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down on your knees!\NGet a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:55.64,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:58.95,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:02.22,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:05.62,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:09.05,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:12.49,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:15.85,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:24.43,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapon... I have it all!

Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這眼神算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被蹂躪得這麼慘還沒學乖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼鄙視我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 把那個耍刀的解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒人來買你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就把你送到 從早到晚都磕藥磕個完的變態那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙不來點激烈的SM滿足不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你被他用藥調教了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天搖著屁股連大便都吃的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你思維也會有所改善的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你的錄像出來了 我也會買上一盤的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡 賭輸了就亂發彪嗎 白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你帶「芝寶」了嗎 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.91,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（芝寶：Zippo 打火機）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來你聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙結果還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吵啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真弄不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我親愛的萊薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well,my dear Revy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到這裡來幹吧呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和我上床嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you did wanna fuck,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真高興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿銀 阿銀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢在太歲頭上動土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想見識我的刀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就全員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手拉著手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下極樂淨土去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺光他們 寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them all BABY！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 看吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種亂戰我還沒從見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別躲起來讓他們見識下男人氣概
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起來跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's all yours
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下不動真格的不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雪緒這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點跟來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼 疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 那女人好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能在這得到和她對干的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不準備準備舞台怎行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰放的什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗髮精？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我投降 我投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give GiveGiveGive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.52,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Give：Give Up 投降）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給？ 給我什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give? Give me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can not speak…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想給我什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your gonna give me something right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well come on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你他媽到底想說些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck are trying so say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 我說我Give了啦 真的 Give GiveGiveGive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵了 你這蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quit yapping you goofball
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底給還是不給 來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna give it to me or not? Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 大塊頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jumbo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The gams's up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在情況一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boy we made a mess
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只好徹底掃蕩一遍這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we got left is to mop-up the place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們分頭行動 把那頭豬和公主搜出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後沿著走廊在泳池會合 OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到我家洛克的話也一起帶過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他幹得好的話 說不定和公主一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼交給你了哦 搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以理解的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽中下下籤了啊 真是可憐你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也別想活著從這出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是地獄旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.24,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（地獄旅館：美國恐怖電影Motel Hell中的地獄旅館）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被黑人吃掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.50,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（黑人：指劇中殺人鬼 Michael.Melvin）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是打野鴨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永生去吧 寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time to live forever Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音 聽不到聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火槍 難道其他人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 火槍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽見了啦 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？恐怕都死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠跟你混了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空說廢話 就去找那女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我怎麼辦啊 計劃都支離破碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 想開溜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是令人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你會殺手下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,評價越來越低了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你還這麼生龍活虎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是還沒遇到那大塊頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女槍手還是第一次見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於有機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我睡一晚吧 小萊薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為的就是這個？ 笑死人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:08:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這罐子落地那刻就是開始信號哦 小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 十 九 八 七
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為自己是西部槍手跟我對決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰有時間陪你這連三流都不如的賤貨 蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很想殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要是恨不得不被我殺就要另當別論了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定由大塊頭處理你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婊子 你媽地站住 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 賤貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 我叫你站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓你久等了 大塊頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting,jumbo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你想見的傢伙帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you,your prom date
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真他媽沒趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你蒼蠅啊 耍刀的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐早就不在了 被我殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了？ 那就快給我滾回去烤你的章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你這種有點小聰明的小狗仔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能偷到錢袋裡的錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子…有種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 讓我見識一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撥槍的時機由你選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了你 我殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜下來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊薇和銀次先生似乎幹得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一 再等一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡島先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要來這？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從知道你被「我們的工作」捲了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一無所知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我被「捲了進來」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說錯了 岡島先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是站在那中心的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪緒 你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡島先生 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承了鷲峰組第十四代總代的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便是鷲峰組實質上的最高權力者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不是被捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是原本就站在那中心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你 是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是明知「這邊」是什麼樣的地方還踏進來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了吧 充滿惡意不懂分辨事物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種人在背叛 廝殺著 就是這樣的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡島先生 我再問一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為何而來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我剛才說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看著你被捲進來而置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置之不理？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為板東的死是自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當然也在場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織失去推進力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與頂上的組織疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須與強大的勢力對抗之時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能救其出苦境的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結拜弟兄的復權
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不承認親屬以外之人的繼承
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則就是這樣定的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼想 這都是故意找碴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管這是多麼無理的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也只剩這一條路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們黑道的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的人生又怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不希望這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,板東 阿銀 連你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家為了使你遠離爭鬥而拼盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你不站在「這」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 我能來「這」更早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 該恨的是香砂會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 只是強迫自己一個人背負責任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的只有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得在咖啡屋談的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 與篩子是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個法國人說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人啊 要把自己扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往自己決定的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是被逼 而是自己選擇了它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為父親 為追隨父親的人盡我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是不得不選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你看這步看錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就必須把多餘的東西也一同背負
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你站在黃昏下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你一直停留在黃昏下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能往「這」來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「自己選的」不這樣想怎能作出覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人的生命 名譽 未來都關係在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我除了為這些戰鬥還有什麼選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是自己想「自己選的」 就不可能撐得下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 相信那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只到由於莫須有的罪名 被巡警打個半死的那晚上為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果你再提回正常位的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就不再是同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與那個時候 沒有分別
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這孩子經歷的這晚經驗面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對這個在自己眼前滾落到你們那邊的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無言以對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 就在我站在的這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在除此之外的任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腳 根本沒站在任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個…鬼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然覺得給你的死法是有點便宜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過程度正好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了 發生的事情全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事 壞事都由我來背負
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣大家與阿銀都能得救的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪緒 你對阿銀…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡島先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼站在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在咖啡屋時說的話 其實我當時並不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可現在我想我能明明白白跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是為什麼逃入東南亞的黑社會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你還想追求日本 不 想追求日常生活中的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最後你其實什麼都沒有選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有回到平穩的每日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有踏進充滿罪惡的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 在這止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經說過 你想救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救鷲峰組 救阿銀 救所有的組員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能做得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你 並非想救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是不想失去本被丟掉的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果對我見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你對日本留下的追憶就會連最後的碎片都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都沒背負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連對本被自己丟掉的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還抱著一絲憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的你 到底能保護誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的你 到底能拯救誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 來 回答我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想普通活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與不想痛苦活下去的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應該站在同樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪緒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在不甘心忍受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我 討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:19:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹了件很有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子彈哦 寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把子彈斬成了兩半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能再讓我看一次啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能心急
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和翻譯對我有恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必白白浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 運氣差的話 總會有幹架的機會的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪緒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次真是萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我 希望今後永不要相見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克還沒回房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 在哪兒磨蹭呢
